engineers you've got to have accountants you've

06:37.910 --> 07:06.465
got to have statisticians you've got to have 
bankers financiers and businessmen and those are

06:37.910 --> 07:06.465
the KPM people they must be included in a coalition 
as well also and this is not unimportant they're

06:37.910 --> 07:06.465
the people who speak the best to foreigners. 
